---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContentHero from '../../components/ContentHero.astro';
import TakeAction from '../../components/TakeAction.astro';
---

<Layout title="Buy more land for restoration">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<ContentHero
		title="Buy more land for restoration"
		imgSrc="/hero-land-fund.jpg"
		imgAlt="Green rolling hills with patches of trees and stone fences"
	/>

	<!-- Main Content with Donorbox Widget -->
	<section class="PageSection" data-layout="sidebar-right">
		<div class="PageSection__content">
			<!-- Left: Main Content (67%) -->
			<div>
				<div class="prose">
					<p>
						Protect Earth does a lot more than just plant trees - we create lasting, thriving
						woodlands, wetlands, and ecosystems. This fund was set up to provide confidence that
						every penny was going to purchasing land, and not admin costs or CEO bonuses.
					</p>
					<p>
						We love collaborating with landowners and farmers - so far, we've helped over 60 farms,
						hotels, local councils, schools, parks, and even wedding venues bring more trees to
						their land. But some of our most exciting work happens when we create whole new diverse
						nature reserves, linking up multiple types of habitat.
					</p>
					<p>Thanks to generous donations, we've purchased three amazing sites:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<a href="/sites/high-wood">High Wood</a> - A flourishing ancient woodland where wildlife
							is returning thanks to your support.
						</li>
						<li>
							<a href="/sites/goytre-wood">Goytre Wood</a> - Ex grazing upland in Powys that's being returned
							to a thriving woodland, with skylards protected on the grassland.
						</li>
						<li>
							<a href="https://warleighnaturereserve.org/" target="_blank"
								>Warleigh Nature Reserve</a
							> - An 84 acre mixture of wetlands, ancient woodland, grassland, and beaver habitat that
							you helped us purchase for £630,000, with £250,000 in debt which needs to be paid off through
							future Land Fund donations.
						</li>
					</ul>
					<p>
						With your support, we can buy more land, create more forests, and begin landscape-scale
						restoration with our new neighbours, and protect more nature - permanently.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>
							Every pound donated to the Land Fund goes directly toward securing and restoring new
							woodlands and ecosystems.
						</strong>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Right: Donorbox Widget (33%) -->
			<div>
				<div class="sticky">
					<script src="https://donorbox.org/widget.js" paypalExpress="true"></script>
					<iframe
						src="https://donorbox.org/embed/protect-earth?language=en"
						name="donorbox"
						allowpaymentrequest="allowpaymentrequest"
						seamless="seamless"
						frameborder="0"
						scrolling="no"
						height="700px"
						class="w-full"
						style="min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important"
						allow="payment"></iframe>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TakeAction />
</Layout>
